  "question": [
    "If $P=\\begin{bmatrix}1&a&3\\\\ 1&3&3\\\\ 2&4&4\\end{bmatrix}$ is the adjoint of a $3\\times3$ matrix A and $|A|=4$, then a is equal to"
  ],
  "choices": [
