      "4"
    ],
    [
      "5"
    ],
    [
      "11"
    ],
    [
      "0"
    ]
  ],
  "correctAnswer": 1,
  "explanation": [
    "Property: $|adj A| = |A|^{n-1}$. Here $n=3$.",
    "$|P| = |A|^2 = 4^2 = 16$.",
    "Calculate determinant of P: $1(12-12) - a(4-6) + 3(4-6) = 0 + 2a - 6$.",
    "$2a - 6 = 16 \\implies 2a = 22 \\implies a = 11$."
